OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,FBy Leah McNally
OL,8,FLast year, a ride on a friend's e-
OL,9,Fscooter ended in a race to A&E.
OL,11,FKirsty Walker's son Cal was placed
OL,12,Finto an induced coma after the
OL,13,Faccident.
OL,15,FIt left him with a fractured skull and
OL,16,Fa tear to the lining of his brain.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV Kirsty said: "That
OL,7,Fwait, not knowing the outcome of what
OL,8,Fwas going to happen, or whether he was
OL,9,Fgoing to make it, because seeing him
OL,10,Fthe way he was, I was just like`he's
OL,11,Fdone, you know, he's gone."
OL,13,FHowever Cal's recovery defied
OL,14,Fexpectations from both his family and
OL,15,Fmedics.
OL,17,FKirsty said: "The next morning, I was
OL,18,Fin the wee camp bed beside him, and he
OL,19,Fliterally just sat up. To hear his
OL,20,Fvoice, you know, because in my head it
OL,21,Fwas like`is he ever going to make it?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"Is he ever going to be able to talk?
OL,7,FIs there going to be brain damage? Is
OL,8,Fthere going to be lasting damage?
OL,10,FShe continued: "He remembers nothing
OL,11,Fat all.
OL,13,F"I kind of was like, I would've liked
OL,14,Fhim to remember a wee bit maybe put
OL,15,Fthat fear into him. Because at the end
OL,16,Fof the day, he's a teenage boy and if
OL,17,Ffriends are out and they're on them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"As long as they're still out and
OL,7,Fabout and on the road, there's a
OL,8,Fchance that any child is going to get
OL,9,Fonto one."
OL,11,FPSNI figures show a trend moving in
OL,12,Fthe wrong direction.
OL,14,FIn the last three years, people
OL,15,Finjured in reported e-scooter
OL,16,Fcollisions has risen by over 60%.
OL,18,FKirsty hopes her experience serves as
OL,19,Fa stark warning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"A lot of people that I know from the
OL,7,Farea and my friends, any of their
OL,8,Fchildren that had any of them, they
OL,9,Fgot rid of them straight away, and I
OL,10,Fdefinitely think that's the route to
OL,11,Fgo," she said.
OL,13,FIn a statement, a Department for
OL,14,FInfrastructure spokesperson said: "It
OL,15,Fis currently illegal to use e-scooters
OL,16,Fon public roads and public spaces
OL,17,Fhere. Anyone using an e-scooter
OL,18,Fillegally may be subject to
OL,19,Fenforcement action by the PSNI.
OL,26,@vD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"The Department is exploring measures
OL,7,Fto raise awareness around the dangers
OL,8,Fassociated with e-scooters.
OL,10,F"The Department is also monitoring the
OL,11,Fprogress of a pilot scheme for rental
OL,12,Fe-scooters in Britain, as well as the
OL,13,Fimpact of the legislative changes in
OL,14,Fthe south which made the use of e-
OL,15,Fscooters legal and regulated their use
OL,16,Fon public roads from May 2024.
OL,18,F"This evidence base can help inform
OL,19,Fthe department of what steps to take
OL,20,Fin relation to the registration and
OL,21,Fregulation of e-scooters."
OL,26,@}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,FIn a statement, the PSNI said: "They
OL,7,Fare working with community partners to
OL,8,Faddress concerns around e-scooter use
OL,9,Fand would appeal to those who own one,
OL,10,Fto put safety first."
OL,12,FWest Belfast Neighbourhood Sergeant
OL,13,FHakin said: "They are not toys, and
OL,14,Fthey can only be ridden on private
OL,15,Fland, not public roads or pavements.
OL,16,FTheir use in public spaces poses a
OL,17,Frisk to the safety of both riders and
OL,18,Fthe public, and someone could be
OL,19,Fseriously hurt as a result of their
OL,20,Finappropriate use.
OL,26,@uD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"To be clear, e-scooters are not
OL,7,Fdefined within law. They are not
OL,8,Fapproved for on-road use and
OL,9,Fconsequently they are regarded as a
OL,10,Fmotor vehicle if found to be driven on
OL,11,Fa road or in another public space.
OL,13,F"This means the driver requires a
OL,14,Fdriving licence and the vehicle must
OL,15,Fbe taxed, insured and fitted with
OL,16,Flights and a number plate. As the vast
OL,17,Fmajority of e-scooters and riders will
OL,18,Fnot be able to comply with these legal
OL,19,Frequirements, they are therefore
OL,20,Frestricted to 'off-road' use only.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"Please help to keep our roads and
OL,7,Fcommunities safe spaces for all by
OL,8,Fthinking carefully about where you use
OL,9,Fyour e-scooter, and the potential
OL,10,Fsafety issues you could be causing
OL,11,Fwithin your own community."
OL,13,FSergeant Hakin continued: "Our
OL,14,FNeighbourhood Policing Teams have
OL,15,Ftargeted patrolling in place in order
OL,16,Fto detect offenders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]uD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772467872
OL,3,CMum warns of e-scooter dangers after
OL,4,Cson was left with brain injury
OL,6,F"We'd also ask that the community
OL,7,Fcontinues to report the illegal and
OL,8,Fdangerous driving of e-scooters so we
OL,9,Fcan help to make our roads safer for
OL,10,Feveryone.
OL,12,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,13,FITVX
OL,15,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
